XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Description: Web server for Bazaar
 Loggerhead is a web viewer for projects in the Bazaar version control system. 
 It can be used to navigate a branch history, annotate files, view patches, 
 perform searches, etc. It's heavily based on bazaar-webserve, which is itself 
 based on hgweb for Mercurial.
